    &lt;h3&gt;Unmasking the Heart&lt;/h3&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Verse 1&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Behind the walls of silent fear,&lt;br&gt;
    Julia hid, year after year.&lt;br&gt;
    Her laughter gone, her voice so small,&lt;br&gt;
    As judgment cast its shadowed pall,&lt;br&gt;
    She stood alone, afraid to call.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;But courage grew within her heart,&lt;br&gt;
    A whispered spark, a place to start.&lt;br&gt;
    She took a step, then two, then more,&lt;br&gt;
    Reaching out to open doors,&lt;br&gt;
    To find the strength she knew before.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chorus&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Unmasking the heart, breaking free,&lt;br&gt;
    A journey toward her destiny.&lt;br&gt;
    Through tears and trials, she found her way,&lt;br&gt;
    To live, to heal, to face each day.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Verse 2&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Through therapy, she learned her name,&lt;br&gt;
    Released from judgment, guilt, and shame.&lt;br&gt;
    Each tear a drop of healing grace,&lt;br&gt;
    Reflecting hope within her face,&lt;br&gt;
    Her spirit found a sacred space.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;With each new day, she found her voice,&lt;br&gt;
    A clearer path, a brighter choice.&lt;br&gt;
    The shadows faded, the light grew near,&lt;br&gt;
    As strength replaced her deepest fear,&lt;br&gt;
    Her purpose found, her soul sincere.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chorus&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Unmasking the heart, breaking free,&lt;br&gt;
    A journey toward her destiny.&lt;br&gt;
    Through tears and trials, she found her way,&lt;br&gt;
    To live, to heal, to face each day.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bridge&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Now Julia stands, her voice a flame,&lt;br&gt;
    A shining light, a lasting name.&lt;br&gt;
    Her scars a map of battles won,&lt;br&gt;
    A guiding star for everyone.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chorus&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Unmasking the heart, breaking free,&lt;br&gt;
    A journey toward her destiny.&lt;br&gt;
    Through tears and trials, she found her way,&lt;br&gt;
    To live, to heal, to face each day.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Outro&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Her tale of courage, her path of grace,&lt;br&gt;
    A beacon bright in every place.&lt;br&gt;
    Unmasking the heart, she stands apart,&lt;br&gt;
    A story of strength, a work of art.&lt;/p&gt;
